### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@reserveId = cmd6ontyx0023oe0rem3vv7b1

### ===== BUSCAR RESERVAS =====

### Obtener reserva por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/{{reserveId}}

### Buscar reservas paginadas
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/paginate?page=1&limit=10

### Buscar reservas por día
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/by-day/reservations?date=2024-07-17&complexId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh&sportTypeId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh

### ===== ELIMINAR RESERVAS =====

### Eliminar reserva por ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reserves/{{reserveId}}

### ===== ACTUALIZAR ESTADO =====

### Cambiar estado a CANCELADO
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reserves/{{reserveId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELADO"
}

### Cambiar estado a CONFIRMADO
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reserves/{{reserveId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMADO"
}

### Cambiar estado a PENDIENTE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reserves/{{reserveId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PENDIENTE"
}

### ===== CREAR RESERVA DE PRUEBA =====

### Crear nueva reserva
POST {{baseUrl}}/reserves
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientName": "Juan Test",
  "clientPhone": "123456789",
  "clientEmail": "juan@test.com",
  "date": "2024-07-18",
  "schedule": "10:00-11:00",
  "complexId": "clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh",
  "courtId": "clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh",
  "sportTypeId": "clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh",
  "price": 15000,
  "status": "PENDIENTE"
}

### ===== ACTUALIZAR RESERVA =====

### Actualizar reserva completa
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reserves/{{reserveId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientName": "Juan Actualizado",
  "clientPhone": "987654321",
  "price": 20000,
  "status": "CONFIRMADO"
}

### ===== CONSULTAS ESPECÍFICAS =====

### Ver horarios disponibles
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/by-day/schedules?date=2024-07-18&complexId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh&sportTypeId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh

### Ver disponibilidad diaria
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/availability/daily?date=2024-07-18&complexId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh&sportTypeId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh

### Ver disponibilidad para horario específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/availability/schedule?date=2024-07-18&schedule=10:00-11:00&complexId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh&sportTypeId=clm6u8trg0000h9nkac7w2bxh

### ===== ENDPOINTS PARA ELIMINACIÓN RÁPIDA =====

### Buscar reservas por nombre de cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/search?clientName=Juan

### Buscar reservas por teléfono
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/search?phone=123456789

### Buscar reservas por fecha
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/search?date=2024-07-17

### Buscar reservas por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/reserves/search?status=PENDIENTE

